name: PRJKTNEON LORE_CONTEST_01
description:
A short story set in the PRJKTNEON universe. An old abandoned cathedral has been repurposed by a strange woman providing medical assistance to those that need it, who cannot afford the extortionate prices set by BioMAX Pharmaceutical Corporation.

Medical supplies are usually provided by one of the city's various mercenary groups, specialising in raids on corporate gigafactories. 

One routine delivery takes a strange turn...
